OL,3,CJailed rogue surgeon defends
OL,4,Ccontroversial procedure during
OL,5,Cinquests of patients
OL,7,FDisgraced surgeon Ian Paterson has
OL,8,Fdefended a controversial procedure
OL,9,Fnamed a 'cleavage sparing mastectomy'
OL,10,Fat an inquest into the death of one of
OL,11,Fhis patients.
OL,13,FThe jailed former consultant, who is
OL,14,Fserving a 20-year sentence for
OL,15,Fwounding ten patients after being
OL,16,Fconvicted in 2017, spoke at the
OL,17,Finquest of Elaine Turbill, who died
OL,18,Faged 63 in 2017.
