OL,3,CJailed rogue surgeon defends
OL,4,Ccontroversial procedure during
OL,5,Cinquests of patients
OL,7,FShe died after her breast cancer
OL,8,Freturned, despite undergoing a
OL,9,Fmastectomy carried out by Paterson in
OL,10,F2005.
OL,12,FIn court, Paterson was described as
OL,13,Fperforming an unauthorised "cleavage-
OL,14,Fsparing" mastectomy on Mrs Turbill and
OL,15,Fother cancer patients, which left
OL,16,Fbehind breast tissue for cosmetic
OL,17,Freasons, but increased the risk of
OL,18,Fcancer returning.
OL,26,@uD@\OUvD@HO]
