OL,4,Ccontroversial procedure during
OL,5,Cinquests of patients
OL,7,FPaterson, who was giving evidence
OL,8,Fremotely from prison to the inquest,
OL,9,Fclaimed it was not him who coined the
OL,10,Fterm "cleavage-sparing mastectomy" and
OL,11,Fsaid the phrase had "caused the
OL,12,Fhysteria".
OL,14,FHe also said that the procedure had
OL,15,Fnot been used on Mrs Turbill as the
OL,16,Fsize and position of her breast tumour
OL,17,Fdid not allow for it.
OL,19,FHe did however admit that he used the
OL,20,Fpractice on others of his patients.
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@bO]sD@UOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/13
