OL,7,FWhen asked by counsel to the inquest,
OL,8,FJonathan Jones KC, whether he had told
OL,9,Fthe woman that this procedure would be
OL,10,Fused, Paterson said no because he felt
OL,11,Fthat it was just an 'adaption of a
OL,12,Fstandard mastectomy' and that when he
OL,13,Fwas told that it could cause extra
OL,14,Frisk and would require specific
OL,15,Fpatient permission in future, he
OL,16,Fstopped doing them.
OL,18,FAsked whether he considered he had
OL,19,Fbeen a good breast surgeon, Paterson,
OL,20,Fwho wore a pale blue shirt with a
OL,21,Fpoppy attached for the hearing, said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
