PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F376A1730486309
OL,3,CJailed rogue surgeon defends
OL,4,Ccontroversial procedure during
OL,5,Cinquests of patients
OL,7,F"I don't think people go around
OL,8,Fassessing themselves but yes, if I
OL,9,Fthought I was a bad breast surgeon I
OL,10,Fshouldn't be doing it, should I?
OL,12,F"You seek help from colleagues if you
OL,13,Ffeel there is something wrong with
OL,14,Fyour technique. You rely on your
OL,15,Fcolleagues to tell if they think there
OL,16,Fis something wrong with your technique
OL,17,F` that's what MDTs (multidisciplinary
OL,18,Fteam meetings) are for."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@XO]
