OL,7,FOne of Paterson's colleagues,
OL,8,Fradiologist Dr Chris Fletcher, told
OL,9,Fthe inquest on Wednesday (30th
OL,10,FOctober) that the breast surgeon was a
OL,11,F"nightmare" to work with, and that
OL,12,Fmultidisciplinary meetings between NHS
OL,13,Fcolleagues to discuss the treatment of
OL,14,Ftheir patients were "always difficult"
OL,15,Fbecause Paterson "always tried to run
OL,16,Fthe show".
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@KO]vD@UOUvD@fO]wD@ROUxD@IO]
