OL,7,FWhen asked on Thursday what his
OL,8,Frecollection of the meetings was,
OL,9,FPaterson admitted there were
OL,10,F"tensions" but said they largely
OL,11,Frelated to the heavy workload they had
OL,12,Fto deal with.
OL,14,FHe added that there were also tensions
OL,15,Fbetween himself and colleague Dr
OL,16,FAndrew Stockdale, who raised concerns
OL,17,Fabout the amount of residual tissue
OL,18,Fthat was being left behind by Paterson
OL,19,Fduring his mastectomies.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
