OL,3,CJailed rogue surgeon defends
OL,4,Ccontroversial procedure during
OL,5,Cinquests of patients
OL,7,FHe said "(Dr Stockdale) expressed his
OL,8,Fviews outside the MDT, he decided he
OL,9,Fwould collect a cohort of patients he
OL,10,Ffelt exhibited his concerns and
OL,11,Finstead of sharing them with me or the
OL,12,FMDT, he shared them with a third
OL,13,Fparty."
OL,15,FWhen asked if he agreed with Dr
OL,16,FStockdale that there was residual
OL,17,Ftissue left behind during the
OL,18,Fmastectomies he performed, Paterson
OL,19,Fsaid "We're getting onto the concept
OL,20,Fof the cleavage-sparing mastectomy.
OL,26,@oD@IOUuD@GO]{D@FOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/13
