OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F376A1730486309
OL,3,CJailed rogue surgeon defends
OL,4,Ccontroversial procedure during
OL,5,Cinquests of patients
OL,7,F"It wasn't me who coined that phrase,
OL,8,FI think he did. A CSM is the thing
OL,9,Fthat seems to have created the
OL,10,Fhysteria, the furore, whatever you
OL,11,Fwant to call it.
OL,13,F"For a limited number of patients, it
OL,14,Fwas possible, if the cancer was
OL,15,Fcentral or lateral and they had a
OL,16,Flarger than average breast, it was
OL,17,Fpossible to leave slightly thicker
OL,18,Fflaps.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/13
