OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F376A1730486309
OL,3,CJailed rogue surgeon defends
OL,4,Ccontroversial procedure during
OL,5,Cinquests of patients
OL,7,F"A thicker flap doesn't leave breast
OL,8,Ftissue behind. No breast surgeon will
OL,9,Fever tell you 100% of breast tissue is
OL,10,Fremoved during a mastectomy, it is
OL,11,Fnonsense. No mastectomy is ever fully
OL,12,Fcomplete.
OL,14,F"No surgeon aims to leave breast
OL,15,Ftissue after a mastectomy, that's just
OL,16,Fcrazy."
OL,18,FPaterson said he did not specifically
OL,19,Fremember Mrs Turbill, but was asked by
OL,20,FMr Jones whether he would have
OL,21,Fexplained to her what a mastectomy was.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUxD@GO]
