OL,3,CJailed rogue surgeon defends
OL,4,Ccontroversial procedure during
OL,5,Cinquests of patients
OL,7,FHe said "Most ladies know what a
OL,8,Fmastectomy is, I never went into great
OL,9,Fdetail, it scares them and I don't
OL,10,Fthink they hear it, they just hear the
OL,11,Fword cancer.
OL,13,F"Not long after the diagnosis and the
OL,14,Fplan, this lady would have been taken
OL,15,Finto a separate room with a breast
OL,16,Fcare nurse and would have discussed
OL,17,Fthings in more detail.
OL,19,F"We leant on our breast care nurses a
OL,20,Flot for information delivery."
OL,26,@oD@IOUuD@AOU{D@AOU|D@^O]
